com.intel.device.api.sensor

Class SensorCalibrationConfigRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.device.api.sensor.SensorCalibrationConfigRequest

  • @Immutable
 @NotThreadSafe
public class SensorCalibrationConfigRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines a data structure to be sent to the wearable to perform a specific sensor calibration It is very similar to SensorCalibrationConfig which serves for calibration info received from the wearable. Only 4 possible calibrations are currently supported and each has a static newInstance method to prevent invalid calibration requests creation
